description: This stunning 2-level penthouse condo near Telegraph Hill offers breathtaking city views and luxury living. The top floor features a spacious bonus room with a wet bar, leading to a private roof deck showcasing panoramic views of the Boston skyline, including Back Bay and Downtown. The freshly finished hardwood floors throughout add a modern touch to the open floor plan. The expansive primary suite boasts a large bedroom, a walk-in closet, and a spa-like bathroom with a soaking tub, and double vanity. Perfect for entertaining and relaxing, this penthouse combines comfort and elegance in an unbeatable location.
